<h2 class="bold font-l">The titular Little Inferno</h2>
<p class="_pmvv-vidbox-descTxt">
The eponymous fireplace of Little Inferno is powerful enough to consume virtually anything in its fires, and the player is encouraged to throw in things like batteries and chainsaws. </p>
</div>
<div class="video-examples-thumbs">
<a href="#video-link" data-video-id="4q3uup" data-video-descrip="The Bop-It transforms into a gun and has plans of killing a senator." data-video-title="Evil Bop-It" data-video-url="https://d1w6li7s85ibls.cloudfront.net/qvbr/4q3uup_640x360p_qvbr.mp4" data-video-thumbnail="https://static.tvtropes.org/trope_videos_transcoded/images/sd/4q3uup.jpg" data-video-trope="Main/MyLittlePanzer" data-video-tropename="My Little Panzer" data-video-approval="APPROVED" data-video-troper-rating="" data-video-average-rating="" data-video-rating-count="" data-video-media-sources="WesternAnimation/RobotChicken" class="video-launch-link video-overlay-link video-background-image lazy-image" data-src="https://static.tvtropes.org/trope_videos_transcoded/images/sd/4q3uup.jpg">
<p><span class="bold">Evil Bop-It</span></p>
</a>
